WEBVTT

02:11.714 --> 02:13.258
- Hello?
-  <i>Carmen?</i>

02:14.092 --> 02:15.009
Yeah?

02:15.093 --> 02:16.594
<i>Hi, it's Griselda.</i>

02:19.097 --> 02:20.890
Griselda? You okay?

02:20.974 --> 02:24.978
Listen, I know it's been a while,
but I need a favor.

02:25.061 --> 02:26.354
<i>What's going on?</i>

02:27.730 --> 02:29.899
Something just happened
between me and Alberto

02:29.983 --> 02:33.194
and I thought if anyone would understand--

02:33.278 --> 02:34.779
<i>Oh, honey. I'm sorry.</i>

02:34.863 --> 02:36.322
You wanna talk about it?

02:36.406 --> 02:38.408
<i>Yeah, when I get there.</i>

02:39.033 --> 02:41.035
Here? You're coming to Miami?

02:41.119 --> 02:44.080
With the kids. You have an extra room.

02:44.164 --> 02:45.165
<i>Right?</i>

02:46.040 --> 02:49.419
Yeah, but it's really small.

02:49.502 --> 02:51.171
<i>We'll be there in the morning.</i>

02:52.130 --> 02:55.008
Carmen. Thank you so much.

02:59.971 --> 03:01.139
Shit.

03:05.476 --> 03:06.311
Ready.

03:07.562 --> 03:08.646
Mom--

03:08.730 --> 03:11.816
It's so early.
Couldn't we take a later flight?

03:11.900 --> 03:13.818
- Are you fucking packed?
- Yes.

03:17.155 --> 03:19.949
- What about Alberto?
- I'll explain in the car.

03:20.992 --> 03:22.035
Where's Ozzy?

03:22.118 --> 03:24.454
Not sure. In the bathroom?

03:27.874 --> 03:30.501
Ozzy, we have to go now!

03:30.585 --> 03:33.922
Just a minute, I have to poop before I go
on the plane and it won't come out.

03:34.005 --> 03:35.340
Hurry!

03:42.680 --> 03:43.514
Let's go.

04:03.868 --> 04:04.702
Mom.

04:06.329 --> 04:08.206
Alberto and I are getting a divorce.

04:09.707 --> 04:12.085
And we're moving to Miami.

04:13.628 --> 04:15.797
I hated that fuck face anyways.

04:15.880 --> 04:18.091
Don't talk about your father like that.

04:18.174 --> 04:19.300
He's not my father.

04:19.384 --> 04:22.637
Dixon, I don't need
the fucking attitude right now.

04:23.680 --> 04:25.431
You need to work on your English.

04:27.517 --> 04:28.977
I don't want to go to Miami.

04:30.645 --> 04:31.854
I know, baby.

04:32.981 --> 04:34.399
But everything will be all right.

05:42.008 --> 05:43.217
This is it.

05:49.599 --> 05:52.894
- Carmen, your house is beautiful.
- Thank you. It's getting there.

05:54.353 --> 05:56.189
I can't believe you're really here.

05:56.814 --> 05:57.732
Me neither.

05:58.900 --> 06:01.069
You wouldn't believe
the fucking day I've had.

06:01.944 --> 06:04.906
We'll talk, all right?
Let me show you the room. Come on.

06:05.990 --> 06:06.824
Come on.

06:08.951 --> 06:10.119
This is the room.

06:14.499 --> 06:15.374
It's great.

06:15.458 --> 06:17.251
One of you can sleep in the chair.

06:17.335 --> 06:18.169
Fuck that.

06:18.252 --> 06:19.087
Dixon!

06:19.796 --> 06:21.339
I'm sorry, long flight.

06:21.422 --> 06:24.717
No, it's okay. I wouldn't want
to sleep on that chair either, Dixon.

06:26.094 --> 06:28.638
So, um, how long do you think
you'll be staying?

06:28.721 --> 06:30.932
Just until I get on my feet.

06:31.015 --> 06:32.016
Find a place.

06:32.100 --> 06:33.392
I hope it's okay with you.

06:33.476 --> 06:35.812
Of course. I'll let you get settled.

06:36.646 --> 06:38.648
Stop it, Dixon!

06:38.731 --> 06:39.565
Enough!

06:39.649 --> 06:41.150
Listen, please.

06:42.276 --> 06:45.488
Soon as I can afford
our own place, we'll leave.

06:45.571 --> 06:47.907
- I promise.

06:47.990 --> 06:51.994
In the meantime,
I need you to be good guests.

06:52.078 --> 06:54.288
Don't be assholes.

06:54.372 --> 06:58.376
No cursing,
and put the fucking toilet seat down.

07:00.002 --> 07:01.712
Mom, how do you know her?

07:01.796 --> 07:03.631
You guys met her in Colombia.

07:03.714 --> 07:08.302
Alberto and I used to hang out
with her when we'd go to New York.

07:09.345 --> 07:10.680
Why doesn't she speak Spanish?

07:10.763 --> 07:15.309
She grew up here. That's what happens.

07:15.393 --> 07:17.437
I don't wanna speak English all the time.

07:17.520 --> 07:18.896
I know.

07:19.939 --> 07:21.566
Check this out.

07:22.442 --> 07:23.443
"Fuck you."

07:23.526 --> 07:25.570
All you need to know.

07:25.653 --> 07:28.990
You don't need to speak English
to know she doesn't want us here.

07:29.740 --> 07:30.575
I know, dear.

07:31.117 --> 07:32.660
I'm working on that.

07:38.040 --> 07:40.460
I still can't believe you're here.

07:41.252 --> 07:42.462
Me either.

07:42.545 --> 07:44.881
I know it's a lot to ask.

07:44.964 --> 07:47.216
So, I just want you to know
that if you have a problem,

07:47.300 --> 07:48.634
I can just find a motel and--

07:48.718 --> 07:50.178
No, Griselda, it's not that.

07:50.261 --> 07:52.513
You know I sympathize
with what you're going through.

07:52.597 --> 07:56.309
My divorce from Reynaldo
was fucking brutal, okay?

07:57.351 --> 07:58.186
But--

07:58.269 --> 08:01.606
You don't want me bringing
that shit back around you, I get it.

08:01.689 --> 08:04.484
There's a lot of women
who leave the man, not the life.

08:05.401 --> 08:07.278
You don't know what he did to me.

08:08.696 --> 08:09.530
He hit you?

08:10.198 --> 08:11.532
Worse.

08:12.992 --> 08:14.202
Listen, Carmen.

08:14.285 --> 08:19.874
I didn't call you just because
we had so many good times together.

08:21.709 --> 08:24.462
I called you because I saw what you did.

08:25.046 --> 08:27.423
You didn't just tell Reynaldo to fuck off.

08:28.090 --> 08:30.885
You came out. You did your thing.

08:30.968 --> 08:33.721
Now you have your own travel agency.

08:33.804 --> 08:34.639
It...

08:35.264 --> 08:36.766
It's fucking inspiring.

08:38.559 --> 08:41.395
All that time as a stewardess
had to count for something.

08:41.479 --> 08:43.773
You know, that's what I want too.

08:44.690 --> 08:45.525
What?

08:47.818 --> 08:49.028
A business of my own.

08:51.072 --> 08:55.076
After all that I have been through,
I swear, Carmen,

08:56.244 --> 08:59.413
I am fucking out of the drug business.

09:04.335 --> 09:06.712
Why don't you come work
with me at the agency?

09:08.839 --> 09:11.759
You know, to help you get started.
See how a business runs.

09:13.344 --> 09:14.470
What time do we start?

09:15.096 --> 09:17.557
8:00 a.m. And don't be fucking late.

09:17.640 --> 09:21.727
Someone's gonna really enjoy
being my fucking boss.

09:22.645 --> 09:27.108
To Alberto and Reynaldo.
May they one day get what they deserve.

09:27.817 --> 09:29.819
I'll fucking drink to that.

10:40.222 --> 10:41.140
Hm.

10:59.367 --> 11:04.413
If we can get 65 kilos
out of this paste, the boss will love us.

11:04.497 --> 11:06.415
That's why you study math, right?

11:06.499 --> 11:07.333
Arturo?

11:08.542 --> 11:09.377
It's your mom.

11:09.460 --> 11:10.711
Oh, dear...

11:10.795 --> 11:11.629
On the phone.

11:11.712 --> 11:13.214
She just doesn't stop.

11:21.347 --> 11:23.599
- Mom, I've told you--
-  <i>Arturo, it's me.</i>

11:26.435 --> 11:28.938
What the fuck, Griselda!
You shouldn't be calling me.

11:29.021 --> 11:30.439
Are you and the boys okay?

11:30.523 --> 11:32.817
<i>Yes, I'm fine. We're fine.</i>

11:32.900 --> 11:34.610
Does he know where I'm at?

11:34.693 --> 11:37.113
- Nobody knows, and don't tell me--
<i>- I'm in Miami.</i>

11:37.196 --> 11:38.239
Fuck.

11:43.035 --> 11:46.330
He doesn't know where you are,
but he has people looking for you.

11:46.997 --> 11:50.334
What about you? Did they rough you up?

11:50.418 --> 11:54.713
No, I'm just the accountant.
And I told them the truth. I didn't know.

11:54.797 --> 11:56.257
<i>Thank God.</i>

11:56.340 --> 11:57.675
Arturo, listen.

11:57.758 --> 11:59.009
I got out with a kilo.

11:59.093 --> 12:00.761
<i>And I need to sell it.</i>

12:01.470 --> 12:03.973
I can stay here and start over again.

12:04.557 --> 12:06.517
Build my own thing.

12:06.600 --> 12:08.185
<i>I think it's time.</i>

12:08.269 --> 12:10.688
Is that a good idea?

12:11.355 --> 12:13.566
The best I've had in a while.

12:13.649 --> 12:19.613
<i>Remember that guy, Manny Suarez,
who used to buy coke from Fernando?</i>

12:19.697 --> 12:21.740
Yeah, the Miami guy. He's dead.

12:21.824 --> 12:28.372
<i>Yeah, but he used to talk about
a spot up here where all the action was.</i>

12:28.456 --> 12:29.373
The Mutiny.

12:30.749 --> 12:31.709
The Mutiny.

12:33.586 --> 12:34.587
That's right.

12:34.670 --> 12:37.798
Sweetie, I'm going
to share some advice with you.

12:39.884 --> 12:40.801
Be careful.

12:41.552 --> 12:43.846
<i>You got nobody looking out for you.</i>

12:45.055 --> 12:48.476
I've never had
anyone looking out for me except you.

12:50.394 --> 12:52.480
Gotta go. I'll talk to you soon.

12:52.563 --> 12:56.025
- If you want, I could come over--

12:57.318 --> 13:00.571
-  How was lunch?
- It was fine. Any customers?

13:00.654 --> 13:01.614
Nope.

13:02.490 --> 13:05.075
But the mailman came in.

13:05.743 --> 13:09.705
I tried to sell him on some
Puerto Vallarta ticket, but nothing.

13:09.788 --> 13:12.500
It gets easier.
I can help you with your pitch.

13:12.583 --> 13:17.671
You know, I do need all the help
you can give me with that. Yes, please.

13:17.755 --> 13:21.383
Okay, good. Take your lunch.
Coffee shop around the corner is good.

13:21.467 --> 13:23.177
- Okay?
- Okay, yeah.

13:37.608 --> 13:38.609
Wipe that again.

13:39.777 --> 13:40.653
It's not clean.

13:44.114 --> 13:46.951
Get your eyes checked, asshole.

13:50.621 --> 13:51.622
You Colombian?

13:54.500 --> 13:55.334
Yeah.

13:56.293 --> 13:59.755
But I came to America to wash dishes.

14:01.423 --> 14:02.466
I know the feeling.

14:25.906 --> 14:26.740
Hi!

14:34.039 --> 14:37.918
<i>♪ Sittin' here
Eatin' my heart out waitin' ♪</i>

14:38.002 --> 14:40.421
<i>♪ Waitin' for some lover to call ♪</i>

14:42.047 --> 14:45.843
