15:13.203 --> 15:15.039
<i>♪ I want some hot stuff ♪</i>

15:16.790 --> 15:22.129
<i>♪ I need hot stuff ♪</i>

15:32.890 --> 15:33.891
-  Oh, shit--

15:33.974 --> 15:35.517
Oh, I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

15:35.601 --> 15:37.645
Fuck! That was full.

15:37.728 --> 15:40.856
It's all right.
Hey, I'm going to buy you another one.

15:41.815 --> 15:42.650
Okay?

15:43.984 --> 15:44.818
Problem solved.

15:45.653 --> 15:47.321
<i>Coral Gables Travel.</i>

15:47.404 --> 15:49.573
I think I know that place.

15:49.657 --> 15:52.993
Maybe I'll come down there,
buy some tickets to Rio.

15:53.077 --> 15:53.994
Expensive.

15:54.078 --> 15:55.037
That's no problem.

15:55.120 --> 15:57.873
Shit, I practically live
in a suite upstairs here.

15:59.833 --> 16:03.170
Then I guess you like
the finer things, huh?

16:05.714 --> 16:07.549
Fuck.

16:08.342 --> 16:10.636
- I bumped into the right chick.

16:11.428 --> 16:14.515
- It's not your skinny gringo lines.

16:15.891 --> 16:18.018
No problem, mama. No problem.

16:21.397 --> 16:22.982
What's going on back there?

16:24.692 --> 16:27.778
Rafo Rodriguez. Call him Amilcar.

16:28.946 --> 16:30.489
You work for him?

16:30.572 --> 16:34.034
We all work for him, mama.
In one way or another.

16:34.118 --> 16:34.994
Mm.

16:38.580 --> 16:40.207
Oh, fuck.

16:40.290 --> 16:42.251
Ooh!

16:43.502 --> 16:44.712
You know your shit.

16:44.795 --> 16:46.839
Not the garbage you're used to, huh?

16:46.922 --> 16:49.383
Hmm, yeah. Mmm.

16:54.555 --> 16:59.435
You know, I might even
be able to sell you a kilo.

16:59.518 --> 17:02.688
Hold on. You some kind
of dealer now or something?

17:04.148 --> 17:06.900
Do I look like a dealer to you?

17:07.484 --> 17:09.319
And what makes you think I'm buying?

17:10.195 --> 17:13.157
- Now, I've seen your type.
- Huh?

17:13.240 --> 17:16.618
- Yeah, nice clothes, walk a little...
- Hmm.

17:16.702 --> 17:19.496
- Little too fast, talk a little too much.
- Mm-hmm.

17:20.372 --> 17:22.666
You need the work. I respect that.

17:24.209 --> 17:27.963
- Hot damn. Kojak with titties.

17:31.133 --> 17:32.885
- You know what?
- Hmm?

17:34.636 --> 17:37.014
I got a better idea. Come with me, mama.

17:42.436 --> 17:44.104
Let me do the talking, okay?

17:49.318 --> 17:50.152
Move out of the way.

17:51.195 --> 17:52.154
Who is this?

17:52.237 --> 17:53.822
Get out of the way, you fucking goon!

17:58.827 --> 18:00.996
Damn. Let's go.

18:04.291 --> 18:06.460
Next time, watch your fucking mouth.

18:09.505 --> 18:10.798
What do you want, Johnny?

18:11.965 --> 18:13.801
I've got some coke you've got to try.

18:13.884 --> 18:14.843
What are you doing?

18:14.927 --> 18:18.430
- I'm just giving him a taste. That's it.
- Hey--

18:18.514 --> 18:20.307
Come on, Johnny.
Let the man enjoy his drink.

18:20.390 --> 18:22.309
Boss, we got a kilo of this shit.

18:22.392 --> 18:25.312
Hey, there's no we. It's my coke.

18:25.395 --> 18:28.190
Oh, Johnny, taking mommy's coke again?
Is that what you're doing?

18:28.273 --> 18:29.650
- I'm serious--
- No, I don't want--

18:29.733 --> 18:31.485
- No! Come on. God damn it.
- I'm sorry.

18:31.568 --> 18:32.820
Okay, I'm sorry.

18:32.903 --> 18:33.904
God.

18:33.987 --> 18:35.572
-  Let's go.
-  Mm-mm.

18:37.658 --> 18:38.575
Listen.

18:39.409 --> 18:42.746
I have an uncut kilo,
and I don't give a fuck who buys it.

18:44.081 --> 18:45.249
You Colombian?

18:47.084 --> 18:47.918
Good ear.

18:48.752 --> 18:49.962
You sound like a gringo.

18:50.045 --> 18:51.004
No, no, no.

18:51.672 --> 18:53.757
I came here as a kid from Venezuela.

18:54.341 --> 18:57.719
My dad was a cop, but he didn't like
the politics over there, so--

18:57.803 --> 19:00.597
Cop? What does he think about all of this?

19:00.681 --> 19:01.515
Mm.

19:01.598 --> 19:03.725
Well, his kid is living
the American dream,

19:03.809 --> 19:06.937
and, uh, he's driving
a brand-new Caddy, so...

19:12.234 --> 19:13.694
Sourced from Caquetá.

19:14.236 --> 19:17.406
You can still...
smell the jungle when you heat it.

19:17.489 --> 19:18.323
Mmm.

19:18.407 --> 19:20.993
I smuggled a kilo in my son's suitcase.

19:21.076 --> 19:22.619
Oh, your son's suitcase.

19:22.703 --> 19:24.163
Yeah. He's 11.

19:24.830 --> 19:28.167
Smarter than Johnny,
but as much of a pain in the ass.

19:28.250 --> 19:29.543
Now, that's hard to do.

19:33.922 --> 19:34.756
Oh.

19:34.840 --> 19:38.969
Thirty grand. But for the cop's son, 25.

19:39.052 --> 19:40.137
Mm-hmm.

19:41.805 --> 19:43.849
Uh, look, listen...

19:43.932 --> 19:48.770
...you need to understand that my business
runs on volume, all right?

19:49.938 --> 19:52.858
So what am I going
to do with one kilo, huh?

19:52.941 --> 19:54.693
Hmm? Hmm?

19:57.696 --> 19:59.740
Now get the fuck out of here, okay?

20:00.365 --> 20:02.284
And take this idiot with you.

20:13.962 --> 20:14.796
Hey.

20:15.923 --> 20:17.341
- Where you going?
- Home.

20:17.966 --> 20:20.052
You fucking embarrassed me
in front of my boss.

20:20.135 --> 20:21.929
Come on, you did that on your own.

20:23.263 --> 20:24.514
Give me the fucking kilo.

20:25.891 --> 20:26.725
I don't have it.

20:26.808 --> 20:27.643
No?

20:29.061 --> 20:32.272
Please don't do that. I have three kids
and we lost everything--

20:32.356 --> 20:35.651
They're going to lose their mom
if you don't give me the fucking kilo.

20:38.445 --> 20:39.613
Fucking get it!

20:58.465 --> 21:01.510
Now get the fuck out of here.
And don't come back.

21:17.192 --> 21:18.777
No!

22:06.908 --> 22:07.743
Mom?

22:09.119 --> 22:10.787
Ozzy, you startled me.

22:11.955 --> 22:12.789
Come here.

22:28.889 --> 22:30.223
I miss Alberto.

22:33.935 --> 22:35.270
I know.

22:37.522 --> 22:38.815
I miss my fish too.

22:58.710 --> 23:01.797
Alberto, can't you wait
till we get inside?

23:01.880 --> 23:04.382
Your brother always serves it
like an appetizer.

23:06.635 --> 23:08.512
We're not here for a dinner party.

23:12.099 --> 23:14.518
We lost two more shipments in New York.

23:15.769 --> 23:16.853
Half a million worth.

23:18.855 --> 23:20.982
I told you we should pull back.

23:21.566 --> 23:22.734
You were right, but...

23:23.527 --> 23:26.488
All that matters right now
is Fernando wants his money.

23:27.989 --> 23:31.118
So you'll pay him double
on the next shipment.

23:31.201 --> 23:32.410
We can't.

23:33.662 --> 23:35.831
He's cutting us off.

23:38.125 --> 23:39.835
We will find another source.

23:40.794 --> 23:44.172
No one's gonna hire smugglers
who lose shipments.

23:44.881 --> 23:46.174
We're fucked.

23:46.800 --> 23:48.927
Then why the fuck are we here?

23:51.555 --> 23:53.598
Because he always had a thing for you.

23:56.184 --> 23:57.018
So?

23:58.728 --> 24:00.105
One night, Griselda.

24:02.023 --> 24:04.401
One night with him,
he'll wipe our debt clean.

24:07.320 --> 24:08.488
Are you fucking kidding?

24:08.572 --> 24:11.575
Baby, please.
It's not a big deal if you think about it.

24:12.159 --> 24:15.036
I mean, you used to do this for a living.

24:18.707 --> 24:20.792
- I'm leaving.
- Wait.

24:20.876 --> 24:24.212
I know I should've listened
to you, my brilliant, beautiful wife.

24:25.881 --> 24:29.134
Look what we built,
our business, our family.

24:29.759 --> 24:32.596
Fernando's jealous of what we have.
That's why he wants you.

24:33.180 --> 24:35.891
Any other time, I'd kill him
for even asking for this.

24:37.475 --> 24:39.060
But he's got us.

24:41.021 --> 24:42.814
And only you can save us.

24:43.982 --> 24:45.942
Save the boys.

25:17.140 --> 25:18.308
He's upstairs.

26:13.321 --> 26:14.155
Mom?

26:15.865 --> 26:17.534
When are we leaving this place?

27:29.522 --> 27:31.358
Hi, welcome.

27:31.441 --> 27:32.650
Something to drink?

27:33.401 --> 27:34.486
Coffee, thanks.

28:03.640 --> 28:05.767
Ahhh! What the fuck?

28:05.850 --> 28:09.771
Fucking selling my coke to that guy? Huh?
Does your boss know what you're doing?

28:09.854 --> 28:12.399
What is he going to do to you,
Johnny, when he finds out?

28:14.234 --> 28:17.070
What the hell do you want?

28:17.153 --> 28:18.780
Get me a meeting with that guy.

28:18.863 --> 28:21.658
